INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (9, 'https://api.gqgwr.cn/upload/2f5bfee0f295d45f2fe146c08.jpg', '面试题：说说Git常用的命令有哪些？', '<p><img src=\"https://localhost:3658/upload/e1adcaadecdaf26efb3c1e600.jpg\" style=\"width: 400px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></p><h2 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-size: 1.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(216, 222, 228); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">一、前言</h2><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>git&nbsp;</code>的操作可以通过命令的形式如执行，日常使用就如下图6个命令即可</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></p><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; position: relative; display: inline-block;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://static.ecool.fun//article/98f23790-a850-4745-a6ba-eaeead51f621.png\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif; border-style: none; width: 960px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; position: absolute; inset: 0px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s;\'><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; padding: 0px 4px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\'>预览</div></div></div><p><br></p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>实际上，如果想要熟练使用，超过60多个命令需要了解，下面则介绍下常见的的<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>git&nbsp;</code>命令</p><h2 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-size: 1.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(216, 222, 228); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>二、有哪些</h2><h2 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-size: 1.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(216, 222, 228); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>配置</h2><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>Git&nbsp;</code>自带一个&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>git config</code> 的工具来帮助设置控制&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>Git&nbsp;</code>外观和行为的配置变量，在我们安装完<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>git</code>之后，第一件事就是设置你的用户名和邮件地址</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>后续每一个提交都会使用这些信息，它们会写入到你的每一次提交中，不可更改</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>设置提交代码时的用户信息命令如下：</p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>git config [--global] user.name &quot;[name]&quot;</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git config [--global] user.email &quot;[email address]&quot;</li></ul><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>启动</h3><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>一个<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>git</code>项目的初始有两个途径，分别是：</p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>git init [project-name]：创建或在当前目录初始化一个git代码库</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git clone url：下载一个项目和它的整个代码历史</li></ul><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>日常基本操作</h3><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>在日常工作中，代码常用的基本操作如下：</p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>git init 初始化仓库，默认为 master 分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git add . 提交全部文件修改到缓存区</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git add &lt;具体某个文件路径+全名&gt; 提交某些文件到缓存区</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git diff 查看当前代码 add后，会 add 哪些内容</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git diff --staged查看现在 commit 提交后，会提交哪些内容</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git status 查看当前分支状态</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git pull &lt;远程仓库名&gt; &lt;远程分支名&gt; 拉取远程仓库的分支与本地当前分支合并</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git pull &lt;远程仓库名&gt; &lt;远程分支名&gt;:&lt;本地分支名&gt; 拉取远程仓库的分支与本地某个分支合并</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git commit -m &quot;&lt;注释&gt;&quot; 提交代码到本地仓库，并写提交注释</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git commit -v 提交时显示所有diff信息</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git commit --amend [file1] [file2] 重做上一次commit，并包括指定文件的新变化</li></ul><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>关于提交信息的格式，可以遵循以下的规则：</p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>feat: 新特性，添加功能</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>fix: 修改 bug</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>refactor: 代码重构</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>docs: 文档修改</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>style: 代码格式修改, 注意不是 css 修改</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>test: 测试用例修改</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>chore: 其他修改, 比如构建流程, 依赖管理</li></ul><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>分支操作</h3><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>git branch 查看本地所有分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git branch -r 查看远程所有分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git branch -a 查看本地和远程所有分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git merge &lt;分支名&gt; 合并分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git merge --abort 合并分支出现冲突时，取消合并，一切回到合并前的状态</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git branch &lt;新分支名&gt; 基于当前分支，新建一个分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git checkout --orphan &lt;新分支名&gt; 新建一个空分支（会保留之前分支的所有文件）</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git branch -D &lt;分支名&gt; 删除本地某个分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git push &lt;远程库名&gt; :&lt;分支名&gt; 删除远程某个分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git branch &lt;新分支名称&gt; &lt;提交ID&gt; 从提交历史恢复某个删掉的某个分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git branch -m &lt;原分支名&gt; &lt;新分支名&gt; 分支更名</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git checkout &lt;分支名&gt; 切换到本地某个分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git checkout &lt;远程库名&gt;/&lt;分支名&gt; 切换到线上某个分支</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git checkout -b &lt;新分支名&gt; 把基于当前分支新建分支，并切换为这个分支</li></ul><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>远程同步</h3><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>远程操作常见的命令：</p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>git fetch [remote] 下载远程仓库的所有变动</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git remote -v 显示所有远程仓库</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git pull [remote] [branch] 拉取远程仓库的分支与本地当前分支合并</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git fetch 获取线上最新版信息记录，不合并</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git push [remote] [branch] 上传本地指定分支到远程仓库</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git push [remote] --force 强行推送当前分支到远程仓库，即使有冲突</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>git push [remote] --all 推送所有分支到远程仓库</li></ul><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>撤销</h3><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git checkout [file] 恢复暂存区的指定文件到工作区</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git checkout [commit] [file] 恢复某个commit的指定文件到暂存区和工作区</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git checkout . 恢复暂存区的所有文件到工作区</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git reset [commit] 重置当前分支的指针为指定commit，同时重置暂存区，但工作区不变</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git reset --hard 重置暂存区与工作区，与上一次commit保持一致</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git reset [file] 重置暂存区的指定文件，与上一次commit保持一致，但工作区不变</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git revert [commit] 后者的所有变化都将被前者抵消，并且应用到当前分支</p></li></ul><blockquote style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 1em; color: rgb(87, 96, 106); border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(208, 215, 222); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: pre-line;\'><code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>reset</code>：真实硬性回滚，目标版本后面的提交记录全部丢失了</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: pre-line;\'><code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>revert</code>：同样回滚，这个回滚操作相当于一个提价，目标版本后面的提交记录也全部都有</p></blockquote><h3 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>存储操作</h3><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>你正在进行项目中某一部分的工作，里面的东西处于一个比较杂乱的状态，而你想转到其他分支上进行一些工作，但又不想提交这些杂乱的代码，这时候可以将代码进行存储</p><ul style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git stash 暂时将未提交的变化移除</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git stash pop 取出储藏中最后存入的工作状态进行恢复，会删除储藏</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git stash list 查看所有储藏中的工作</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git stash apply &lt;储藏的名称&gt; 取出储藏中对应的工作状态进行恢复，不会删除储藏</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git stash clear 清空所有储藏中的工作</p></li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px;\'>git stash drop &lt;储藏的名称&gt; 删除对应的某个储藏</p></li></ul><p data-f-id=\"pbf\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;\">Powered by <a href=\"https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1\" title=\"Froala Editor\">Froala Editor</a></p>', 1, 0, 2, 0, '2023-09-05 11:29:52', '2024-03-13 14:06:44');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (12, 'https://api.gqgwr.cn/upload/2f5bfee0f295d45f2fe146c07.jpg', '面试题：怎么实现图片懒加载？', '<p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\' id=\"isPasted\">懒加载是一种网页性能优化的方式，它能极大的提升用户体验。就比如说图片，图片一直是影响网页性能的主要元凶，现在一张图片超过几兆已经是很经常的事了。如果每次进入页面就请求所有的图片资源，那么可能等图片加载出来用户也早就走了。所以，我们需要懒加载，进入页面的时候，只请求可视区域的图片资源。</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>总结出来就两个点：</p><ol style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding-left: 2em; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif;\'>全部加载的话会影响用户体验</li><li style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0.25em;\'>浪费用户的流量，有些用户并不想全部看完，全部加载会耗费大量流量。</li></ol><h1 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin: 24px 0px 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-size: 2em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(216, 222, 228); line-height: 1.25; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>实现方式</h1><h2 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-size: 1.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(216, 222, 228); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>html 实现</h2><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>最简单的实现方式是给&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>img</code> 标签加上&nbsp;<code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0.2em 0.4em; margin: 0px; background-color: rgba(175, 184, 193, 0.2); border-radius: 6px;\'>loading=&quot;lazy&quot;</code>，比如</p><pre style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, \"SF Mono\", Menlo, Consolas, \"Liberation Mono\", monospace; font-size: 13.6px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; overflow: auto; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-radius: 6px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; position: relative;\'><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; color: rgb(197, 200, 198); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 1px; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0px; overflow: auto; border-radius: 0.3em; background: rgb(29, 31, 33);\'><code style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Inconsolata, Monaco, Consolas, \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace; font-size: 13.6px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; border-radius: 6px; display: inline; overflow: visible; line-height: 1.5; overflow-wrap: normal; border: 0px; color: rgb(197, 200, 198); text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 0px 1px; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\'><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; display: inline-block; min-width: 1.25em; padding-right: 1em; text-align: right; user-select: none; color: rgb(124, 124, 124);\'>1</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>&lt;</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(150, 203, 254);\'>img</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(150, 203, 254);\'> </span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(168, 255, 96);\'>src</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>=</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>&quot;</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(249, 238, 152);\'>./example.jpg</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>&quot;</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(150, 203, 254);\'> </span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(168, 255, 96);\'>loading</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>=</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>&quot;</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(249, 238, 152);\'>lazy</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>&quot;</span><span style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; color: rgb(197, 200, 198);\'>&gt;</span></code></div></div></pre><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>该属性的兼容性也还行，大家生产环境可以使用。</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'><br></p><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; position: relative; display: inline-block;\'><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://static.ecool.fun//article/d08ca711-557a-4da4-88c7-8bdcb20a7fab.png\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, tahoma, arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif; border-style: none; width: 960px; height: auto; max-width: 100%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; position: absolute; inset: 0px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); cursor: pointer; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s ease 0s;\'><div style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; padding: 0px 4px; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;\'>预览</div></div></div><p><br></p><h2 style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.25; padding-bottom: 0.3em; font-size: 1.5em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(216, 222, 228); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>js实现原理</h2><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>我们通过js监听页面的滚动也能实现。</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; font-family: \"PingFang SC\", \"microsoft yahei\", tahoma, arial, \"Hiragino Sans GB\", sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(36, 41, 47); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: